---
title: Bone-In Pork Chops and Mushroom-Spinach Cream with Cheddar Mashed Potatoes and Chives
description: Leaving the bones in pork chops helps them retain their juices for more tender meat! Tonight, pork chops get draped in a creamy mushroom and spinach sauce, elevated with a touch of cooking wine. This easy and elegant meal is perfect any day of the week!
